---
title: Not all functionality is reachable with the keyboard
sc: '2.1.1'
severity: High
difficulty: Medium
sample: page-2
---

The contact form contains a custom dropdown that is not reachable with the keyboard. Users who depend on keyboard navigation cannot fully complete the form.

## Recommendation

Use a standard HTML `<select>` element or ensure the custom dropdown is fully operable with the keyboard, including proper ARIA attributes and keyboard interaction.
